# Environment Variables Template for Production
# Copy this file and fill in your actual values for deployment

# Email Configuration (Required for contact forms)
GMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=your-16-character-app-password
EMAIL_TO=destination-email@gmail.com

# Security Configuration
NEXTAUTH_URL=https://your-domain.vercel.app
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your-secret-key-here

# Important Setup Instructions:
# 1. Go to your Google Account settings
# 2. Enable 2-factor authentication  
# 3. Generate an "App Password" for this application
# 4. Never commit the actual .env.local file to version control
# 5. Set these variables in Vercel dashboard: Project Settings > Environment Variables
